<%
distro_string=(
  case @operatingsystem
    when /centos.*/i
      "Based on CentOS #{@operatingsystemrelease}"
    when /scientific.*/i
      "Based on Scientific Linux #{@operatingsystemrelease}"
    when /redhat.*/i
      "Based on RedHat Enterprise Linux #{@operatingsystemrelease}"
    when /suse.*/i
      "Based on Suse Linux Enterprise Server #{@operatingsystemrelease}"
  else
    "Based on GNU Linux"
  end
)
%>
              +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
              <%="Welcome to #{@clustername}".center(45)%>
              <%= distro_string.center(45) %>
              +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

TIPS:

'module avail'            - show available application environments
'module add <modulename>' - add a module to your current environment

'qstat'                   - show summary of running jobs

